### 1. Confirm a Successful Payment
# Pillar 3 (Idempotency) & Pillar 4 (Logging):
# Simulates the bank notifying the Registrar of a successful transfer.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments/confirm
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": 1,
  "referenceNo": "BANK-REF-SUCCESS-001"
}

###

### 2. Reject a Payment (Account Closed)
# Pillar 17 (Registrar Isolation):
# Simulates a failed transfer that needs the Registrar's attention.
POST http://localhost:8080/api/payments/reject
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "paymentId": 2,
  "reason": "ACCOUNT_CLOSED"
}

